    <item>
      <title>韩国因涉嫌朝鲜部署武器而寻求向乌克兰提供武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/seoul-eyes-arms-for-ukraine-over-alleged-north-korean-deployment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，朝鲜向俄罗斯派兵支援乌克兰战争，韩国则提出向乌克兰运送武器的可能性，这凸显了朝鲜半岛分裂状态被卷入冲突的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/seoul-eyes-arms-for-ukraine-over-alleged-north-korean-deployment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 08:51:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯向金砖国家峰会出席者发出信息：带上现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/russia-has-a-message-for-brics-summit-goers-bring-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[虽然俄罗斯总统普京急于在金砖国家峰会上向其他领导人表明俄罗斯正在摆脱西方因乌克兰战争而实施的制裁，但组织者却向外国嘉宾发出了不同的信息——带上现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/russia-has-a-message-for-brics-summit-goers-bring-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 07:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡前领导人的兄弟在英国获得政治庇护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/singapore-ex-leader-s-brother-gets-political-aslyum-in-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡前总理李显龙的疏远兄弟表示，英国政府以“有充分理由担心”遭受迫害为由，向他提供了政治庇护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/singapore-ex-leader-s-brother-gets-political-aslyum-in-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 07:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
